Package: osmanlica-klavye
Version: 1.0.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Pre-Depends: python3
Depends: xkb-data
Maintainer: Yasin Korkmaz <yasinkorkmaz.dev@gmail.com>
Homepage: https://github.com/podeveloper/osmanlica-transkripsiyon-klavye
Description: Ottoman Turkish Transcription Keyboard Layout
 Osmanli Turkcesi transkripsiyon isaretlerini (d with line below, a with
 macron, s with dot below, g with dot above, h with breve below, hamza,
 ayn vb.) kolayca yazmak icin Turkce Q tabanli klavye duzeni.
 .
 AltGr tusu ile transkripsiyon karakterlerine dogrudan erisim saglar.
 Talat Oncu'nun Windows surumunden ilham alinmistir.
